title: Proposal 1: Rebranding & Token Merge
body:
Proposal Summary: In order to improve Wault's foundation, this proposal is for a Token Merge of all three Wault tokens into a single token, and rebranding into a new project.

The new project would be structured differently, bringing some brand new innovative features and a better profit generation model benefiting the entire community of token holders. We would launch this new project with a DAO structure where users would have input into decision-making and improvements from the beginning.

Full info: https://medium.com/waultfinance/governance-first-major-proposal-f2429e7b234c

Do you support this Proposal?
